lood the space with natural light, enhancing the home’s organic feel. Despite its modest size, the kitchen offers ample storage thanks to hidden compartments and floating shelves, demonstrating OWIU’s commitment to maximizing space without sacrificing design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560332\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560332\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen shelves with assorted ceramics, glasses, and pitchers. Counter features wooden boards, a clay pot, a wooden spoon, and a bowl with tomatoes and avocados.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560333\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560333\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-11-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden dining table with chairs, a bowl of fruit, and a hanging light fixture in a modern kitchen setting.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-11-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-11-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/202