.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-13-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-13-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560336\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560336\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with a round white sink, wooden cabinetry, and a wall-mounted mirror. Tiled surfaces in earth tones and a potted plant decorate the space. Door slightly ajar in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560337\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560337\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A roll of toilet paper is suspended on a metal chain attached to the wall next to a plant with large leaves. The background features a tiled wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560338\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560338\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A small wooden cabin with a single window nestled among tall cacti and lush greenery under a clear blue sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe exterior continues the theme of blending functionality with nature. OWIU carefully designed the fencing to accommodate existing trees, creating a fluid relationship between the built environment and the landscape. Outdoor spaces, including a custom patio and furniture from the HAY Balcony Collection, offer additional areas to enjoy the tranquil surroundings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560339\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560339\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A narrow outdoor path with metal railings runs alongside a wooden building. Tall cacti and trees border the walkway, creating a sunlit, natural setting.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560340\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560340\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A green garden lantern hangs from a tree branch with leaves and two yellow fruits. A wooden lattice is in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560341\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560341\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A small wooden cabin with a single window and door sits amidst desert plants, including tall cacti. A curved stone path leads to it, and a small table with chairs is nearby.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to the main residence, OWIU designed a separate office unit on the property. Clad in cedar and oak, similar to the main house, the detached structure offers a quieter, more secluded atmosphere, ideal for focused work or retreat. The office features a large picture window framing the surrounding trees, keeping the occupant connected to the outdoors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560342\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560342\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Small wooden cabin under a tree with a curved path. An open door reveals a glimpse inside. A round table with items sits outside. Sunlight filters through the branches.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560343\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560343\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Open wooden door leading to a minimalist room with a bench and cushions inside a wooden building.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560344\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560344\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-23-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy room with a beige sofa, bookshelves filled with books, a desk with a lamp, and a decorative wall hanging.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-23-810x608.jpg 810w,