-OWIU-25-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-25-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-25-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Echo-Park-Home-ADU-Los-Angeles-OWIU-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on OWIU Design, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.owiu-design.com/work/architecture/echopark-hillhouse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eowiu-design.com.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/justinchung/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eJustin Chung\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u